title: Engine Design Group - iPhone 6s Grip Case | Slim Fit | Ultra Grip | TPU Case for iPhone 6 and 6s
features: ✔️SLIM AND PROTECTIVE: Helps protect your iPhone against damaging drops and impact shock. Helps protect your iPhone against dust, dirt, oil and grime.

✔️FUNCTIONAL AND STRAIGHTFORWARD: Designed and engineered to provide superior protection, fit and finish for your iPhone. Large cutouts allow clear access to the Lightning port, audio ports, speaker and ring switch.

✔️ADDED PROTECTION: Raised perimeter edge protrudes an imperceptible but effective 0.9 mm to help protect the screen against tabletop contact scratches.

description: from Engine Design Group provides protection and personalization for your iPhone, while minimizing added and often unnecessary bulk. The case is designed specifically for iPhone 6s (4.7") 2015, but also works perfectly with iPhone 6 (4.7") 2014. The case is manufactured using high quality TPU that won't break, crack or split, even under extreme conditions. The case is engineered to provide a glove-like perfect fit and features a subtle knurl side texture for added grip. At just 0.7 ounces it has a very high protection to weight ratio.   Helps protect your iPhone against damaging drops and impact shock. Helps protect your iPhone against dust, dirt, oil and grime. Case design nuances, texture, and subtle surface treatments enhance grip. Raised perimeter edge protrudes an imperceptible but effective 0.9 mm to help protect the screen against tabletop contact scratches. Designed and engineered to provide superior protection, fit and finish for your iPhone. Large cutouts allow clear access to the Lightning port, audio ports, speaker and ring switch. Volume and sleep/wake buttons are contour-matched and easy to press. Compatible with all NGN screen protectors, and most glass and plastic stick-on screen protectors. Manufactured with durable, wear-resistant materials. Quality, built to perform and endure.
